init_text:
Once upon a time there was an old mother pig who had one hundred little pigs and not enough food to feed them. So when they were old enough, she sent them out into the world to seek their fortunes. You know the story about the first three little pigs. This is a story about the 92nd little pig.

The 92nd little pig built a house out of depleted uranium. And the wolf was like, "dude."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It was pretty hardcore, but the piggy wasn't playing games.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: So he worked in a nuclear weapons plant and saved up all of his piggy money to buy the best quality material.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He thought that he didn't have anything to worry about.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The wolves were coming and going in their houses.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: So the 92nd little pig called his 100 brothers and sisters over to his house.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The wolves were scared of the nuclear radiation that leaked out of the house.
